{"tid":1565371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反思】極重要，以子之矛攻子之盾","createTime":"2019-09-13T06:20:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T17:06:55.000Z","uid":7484,"like":117,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"d489c4a551a2ab965d55140762ef926d5252904c","tid":1565371,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ya2sm5w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYa2sm5w.jpg&h=767e8d63&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JJ0Q4iT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJJ0Q4iT.png&h=d1d2ba40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我地應該幫佢地宣傳，記唔記得天安門撐警察會文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過天安門太敏感了，有大陸人可能做左被消失<br />\n不過今次唔同愛國商場快閃集會，我地應該幫佢係大陸宣傳<br />\n <br />\n係大陸搞愛國商場快閃集會打卡<br />\n<br />\n1. 如果風氣形成全國商場集會就等於幫佢哋拎返集會權<br />\n<br />\n2.如果打壓，我哋拎黎做文宣再宣傳<br />\n<br />\n3.可以突破防火牆，拎返佢官方微信文，朋友圈轉載宣傳"},{"pid":"ea22fddb3b66d35174cc60f6ad1ae20f4d48cb95","tid":1565371,"uid":123713,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:21:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">913中秋要人!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Tnu54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6Tnu54.jpg&h=d1f0aa7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=15d9310f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各區集合地點!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n油麻地、佐敦、尖沙咀: 梳士巴利公園(太空館附近)<br />\n荃灣、大窩口、青衣: 荃灣公園(海濱長廊)、青衣海濱長廊<br />\n葵興、葵芳、荔景: 林士德遊樂場、葵涌運動場<br />\n美孚: 嶺南之風<br />\n太子、旺角: 花墟公園<br />\n荔枝角、長沙灣: 長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n深水埗: 通州街公園<br />\n油塘、藍田: 油塘道遊樂場<br />\n將軍澳、寶琳、坑口、康城<br />\n中西區（西區、中環、金鐘、半山、山頂）<br />\n灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后、炮台山: 維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌、太古、西灣河、筲箕灣: 沿海旁<br />\n小西灣、杏花邨、柴灣: 柴灣公園<br />\n鑽石山、黃大仙: 黃大仙廣場<br />\n九龍灣、牛頭角、觀塘: 觀塘海濱公園<br />\n大圍、沙田、馬鞍山 : 沙田百步梯<br />\n元朗、天水圍: 天水園公園<br />\n屯門: 屯門公園<br />\n南區: 鴨利洲風之塔公園<br />\n<br />\n仲有獅子山同山頂人鏈!"},{"pid":"36a3a8f679ad6a0184fb7088f25b08763f40a088","tid":1565371,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:21:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"4e23396ec0f2351d02492914c83ed3bab4cb69d1","tid":1565371,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:21:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4981b91692c53fc3d7585bd5211fa75814abfa27","tid":1565371,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:22:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b23ae9d8562c494881477a57cd83d0e913a523f5","tid":1565371,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:22:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d820d48e156756410758a826f649b9debea76f0","tid":1565371,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:24:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"767156151d484e4abbc6a5c01f5f1e32cff232d9","ti